com.slightech.ble.mynt

接口 MyntListener.FoundCallback

  • 封闭类:
    MyntListener

    public static interface MyntListener.FoundCallback
    zh:

    扫描发现回调

    在开启调用搜寻方法 startSearch 之后，设置 扫描发现回调方法，处理发现设备的设备， 对设备进行连接操作，或者已连接设备断线后进行重连操作。

    en:

    Scan found callback

    After the call search method is turned on, the startSearch is set up to find a callback method to handle the device, the device is connected to the device, or the connection operation is performed after the disconnection of the device.

      • foundFailed

        void foundFailed(int errorCode)
        zh:

        发现失败 en:

        Found failure

        参数:
        errorCode - 错误代码，com.slightech.bluetooth.le.LeDeviceScanner#ERROR_* Possible errorCode values are: LeState.ERROR_BLE_NOT_SUPPORTED, LeState.ERROR_BLUETOOTH_NOT_SUPPORTED, LeState.ERROR_BLUETOOTH_OFF, LeDeviceScanner.ERROR_SCAN_FAILED.
        另请参阅:
        BluetoothLeAgent.BluetoothLeCallback.bleScanFailed(int), LeDeviceScanner.LeScanCallback.onLeScanError(int)

      • foundDevice

        void foundDevice(java.lang.String sn,
                 boolean newOne)
        zh:

        发现设备

        扫描发现时，内部有扫描缓存设备列表信息，扫描时到设备会判断是否是已经扫到过的设备。如果不是，会有newOne标记。

        en:

        Discovery device

        When the scan is found, the inside has a scan of the list of device information, and when it is scanned, the device will determine whether the device has been swept. If not, there will be newOne tags.

        参数:
        sn - 设备sn Device serial number
        newOne - 是否新设备 Is new found device

      • foundDeviceRemoved

        void foundDeviceRemoved(java.lang.String sn)
        zh:

        发现设备移除

        发现设备连接、断开、超时、清理等，会被回调此方法。

        en:

        Device removal

        Discovery device connection, disconnection, timeout, cleaning, etc., will be the callback method.

        参数:
        sn - 设备sn Device serial number
